{
  "stem": "321.2",
  "chunk_idx": 14,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.6,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And we studied together, and she taught-- I learned one thing, not only her kindness at that time, which I remember to this day.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "But I went home with her to learn Hebrew.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And there were six brothers and sisters and the grandmother, who was hard of hearing with the [NON-ENGLISH].",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "I learned to respect the Orthodox Jew.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "I learned to go into that area where the Orthodox Jews lived to begin with and the shtreimel and whatever else, you know, the pious-- and I had tremendous respect.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And it was really rubbing shoulders with Orthodox Jews for the first time.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "That was in Germany.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And then again when I met [?",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Hannah, ?] we became very close friends.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And her mother got out also, and her father.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And we became good friends in London.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And then, when later on, after the war, I was a teacher, as I said, the-- after the war, the displaced persons came to England, after-- the concentration camp survivors.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I felt it my duty to help teach English and to integrate and to help there and did some tutoring for the DPs.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "[?",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Hannah ?] at that time went to Israel.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "I became very involved with the displaced persons.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And I realized then that the English were not as kindly to the DPs as they were to us as children, as poor refugees in-- in the '30s.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "They had suffered.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "They had had a war.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "They had had losses.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "They had lost their property, and they'd lost their men.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And I felt it was for Israel to take the DPs in, so I went to Israel with a group of DPs.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "So I guess my Zionistic background from my mother somehow also influenced me indirectly.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "In '50, early '50.",
      "word_count": 4
    }
  ],
